  - `/daftar_task`: Manage active tasks.
- **Admin FIDs**: `1477344` (Farcaster)
- **Case-Insensitive EVM Checks**: ALWAYS use `.toLowerCase()` on both sides when comparing Ethereum/Base addresses.
- **Anti-Leak Policy**: Never output Private Keys or API Keys in plain text. Always use `.env`.

## 6. NEXT-GEN INTEGRATIONS (NEYNAR & FARCASTER)
- **Neynar SIWE Integration**: Use Neynar SIWE to sync the connected Base wallet with the user's Farcaster FID.
- **Neynar Client ID**: `0a715e62-512c-4b04-a51a-58b3ca51795d` (`VITE_NEYNAR_CLIENT_ID`)
