## 13. UI/UX DESIGN & FRONTEND STANDARDS (SENIOR STAFF ENGINEER MODE)
1. **Clean & Rugged:** Modern dark-themed aesthetic. No heavy libraries like Framer-Motion.
2. **Atomic Layout:** 100% responsiveness. Mobile uses bottom-sheets/drawers.
